OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FExceptionally
OL,6,Fwarm into the evening and overnight,
OL,7,Fwith late sunshine for many. However,
OL,8,Fsome western areas may see sporadic
OL,9,Fshowery rain and some thundery
OL,10,Foutbreaks spread erratically
OL,11,Fnortheast, with locally strong, gusty
OL,12,Fwinds, hail and isolated downpours
OL,13,Fpossible here.
OL,14,
OL,15,CFriday:FExceptionally hot in another
OL,16,Fmainly fine day with sunshine, perhaps
OL,17,Fperiodically hazy. Some early low
OL,18,Fcloud in coastal districts clearing.
OL,19,FGusty, thundery downpours possible
OL,20,Finitially, mainly in west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
